author = "A.J. Ali and J.L. Xu and A.M. Ismail and B.Y. Fu and C.H.M Vijaykumar and Y.M. Gao and J. Domingo and R. Maghirang and S.B. Yu and G. Gregorio and S. Yanaghihara and M. Cohen and B. Carmen and D. Mackill and Z.K. Li",
